WEBVTT

00:00:00.160 --> 00:00:02.710
Good morning, family. How are you

00:00:02.710 --> 00:00:02.720
all

00:00:02.720 --> 00:00:04.990
doing today? I'm feeling better, so I

00:00:05.000 --> 00:00:07.269
appreciate your prayers. My throat

00:00:07.279 --> 00:00:09.230
feels stronger, my voice and all that,

00:00:09.240 --> 00:00:11.509
so I appreciate everybody praying for

00:00:11.519 --> 00:00:13.430
me, my wife, and my children.

00:00:13.440 --> 00:00:14.829
It's been some kind of

00:00:14.839 --> 00:00:17.070
virus, but God is good,

00:00:17.080 --> 00:00:20.070
and we're getting better in

00:00:20.070 --> 00:00:20.080
Jesus'name.

00:00:20.080 --> 00:00:23.109
You know, I guess every one of you has

00:00:23.109 --> 00:00:23.119
heard

00:00:23.119 --> 00:00:25.589
so many people talk about what we

00:00:25.599 --> 00:00:27.070
prayed. I told you all that we were

00:00:27.080 --> 00:00:29.749
praying for Pennsylvania, and sure

00:00:29.759 --> 00:00:30.950
enough,

00:00:30.960 --> 00:00:32.869
there was stuff uncovered in

00:00:32.879 --> 00:00:35.229
Pennsylvania this morning. I

00:00:35.239 --> 00:00:36.670
don't watch a lot of the

00:00:36.680 --> 00:00:41.590
news, but somebody sent emails

00:00:41.600 --> 00:00:43.750
to my wife telling her that we

00:00:43.760 --> 00:00:46.470
uncovered things in the spirit and it

00:00:46.480 --> 00:00:49.510
happened in the

00:00:49.510 --> 00:00:49.520
natural—2,000-some-odd

00:00:49.520 --> 00:00:51.549
fake ballots. She was reading

00:00:51.559 --> 00:00:54.270
me the article; it says they found out

00:00:54.280 --> 00:00:57.670
60 percent of all the voting in

00:00:57.680 --> 00:01:01.389
that area was fake. To God

00:01:01.399 --> 00:01:03.229
be the glory; that was in Pennsylvania.

00:01:03.239 --> 00:01:05.109
Ladies and gentlemen, we are making a

00:01:05.119 --> 00:01:07.270
difference in the spirit realm, so I want

00:01:07.280 --> 00:01:09.870
to encourage you all that this is

00:01:09.880 --> 00:01:12.550
working. Of course, prayer works, so

00:01:12.560 --> 00:01:14.670
don't get weary in

00:01:14.670 --> 00:01:14.680
well-doing.

00:01:14.680 --> 00:01:16.590
You say, "I don't see anything,"well,

00:01:16.590 --> 00:01:16.600
it doesn't

00:01:16.600 --> 00:01:17.749
matter what you see. We're not

00:01:17.759 --> 00:01:19.350
moved by what we see; we're not moved by

00:01:19.360 --> 00:01:20.550
what we feel; we're moved by what the

00:01:20.560 --> 00:01:23.069
word of God says. We stand on

00:01:23.079 --> 00:01:25.069
what the word says we can have and we

00:01:25.079 --> 00:01:27.270
can do, and we do whatever the Bible says

00:01:27.280 --> 00:01:29.510
we can do. I want to get excited

00:01:29.520 --> 00:01:31.469
about what God's doing already in

00:01:31.479 --> 00:01:33.469
just a couple of days of prayer with you

00:01:33.479 --> 00:01:35.030
all since I've been back from the

00:01:35.040 --> 00:01:36.910
prayer conference. I'm going to

00:01:36.920 --> 00:01:38.789
start doing things with different

00:01:38.799 --> 00:01:40.270
backgrounds, and I came

00:01:40.280 --> 00:01:43.670
outside in my backyard to take

00:01:43.680 --> 00:01:46.109
this video by my pink bushes because

00:01:46.119 --> 00:01:48.190
I thought it was kind of fun instead of

00:01:48.200 --> 00:01:50.870
doing it in the house. We

00:01:50.880 --> 00:01:54.950
had a politician's wife reach

00:01:54.960 --> 00:01:57.550
out to us asking for prayer.

00:01:57.550 --> 00:01:57.560
It

00:01:57.560 --> 00:01:59.590
sounds like they are

00:01:59.590 --> 00:01:59.600
spirit-filled

00:01:59.600 --> 00:02:01.830
if they watch this channel and

00:02:01.840 --> 00:02:03.830
are Christians who love the Lord,

00:02:03.830 --> 00:02:03.840
because

00:02:03.840 --> 00:02:05.190
they wouldn't be watching any other way,

00:02:05.200 --> 00:02:07.910
I guess. They're asking for prayer

00:02:07.920 --> 00:02:09.669
for his election because he's running

00:02:09.679 --> 00:02:12.110
for office in Oregon,

00:02:12.120 --> 00:02:13.949
of all

00:02:13.959 --> 00:02:16.470
places, where it's very liberal, so he

00:02:16.480 --> 00:02:20.070
needs a lot of prayer. Who

00:02:20.080 --> 00:02:23.869
is this, babe? Darin Harbick.

00:02:23.869 --> 00:02:23.879
Darin Harbick is

00:02:23.879 --> 00:02:26.070
running for state representative

00:02:26.080 --> 00:02:28.790
for House District 12 in Oregon. He's

00:02:28.800 --> 00:02:31.270
running

00:02:33.640 --> 00:02:35.630
for House District 12 in the

00:02:35.630 --> 00:02:35.640
House of

00:02:35.640 --> 00:02:37.869
Oregon. I hope she said

00:02:37.879 --> 00:02:39.750
that loud enough; I'll say it

00:02:39.760 --> 00:02:42.790
again: Darin Harbick is running for state

00:02:42.800 --> 00:02:45.149
representative for House District 12

00:02:45.159 --> 00:02:47.390
here in Oregon.

00:02:47.400 --> 00:02:48.990
We're going to believe God with him

00:02:49.000 --> 00:02:51.350
today that he's going to have favor and

00:02:51.360 --> 00:02:52.790
that the people would come out in a

00:02:52.800 --> 00:02:54.990
liberal state and vote for

00:02:55.000 --> 00:02:56.790
him, because all things are possible

00:02:56.800 --> 00:02:59.149
to him that believe. Folks, I believe

00:02:59.159 --> 00:03:01.350
this is the time that we start to

00:03:01.360 --> 00:03:04.750
see the salt rise up in these

00:03:04.760 --> 00:03:08.470
last days and we become saltier.

00:03:10.120 --> 00:03:12.309
It's time that we become

00:03:12.319 --> 00:03:15.670
the flavor,

00:03:15.680 --> 00:03:17.390
the ones that people are

00:03:17.400 --> 00:03:19.070
looking to, saying, "Man, there's something

00:03:19.080 --> 00:03:20.990
different about them."I'm believing

00:03:21.000 --> 00:03:24.229
that Darin Harbick is going to come to

00:03:24.239 --> 00:03:26.710
a different level with the Lord in all

00:03:26.720 --> 00:03:28.630
of this and be able to help lead those

00:03:28.640 --> 00:03:31.190
liberals out of the darkness like Moses

00:03:31.200 --> 00:03:33.509
did.

00:03:35.480 --> 00:03:37.630
I gave

00:03:37.640 --> 00:03:42.309
the word about the acceleration of war in

00:03:42.319 --> 00:03:45.309
Europe over a year ago.

00:03:45.319 --> 00:03:49.030
I told you I saw the angel

00:03:49.040 --> 00:03:51.710
and the bottomless pit get released, and

00:03:51.720 --> 00:03:54.229
the Lord called this angel the

00:03:54.239 --> 00:03:56.630
great Apollyon. The Lord said it's

00:03:58.519 --> 00:04:00.429
going to be released from that pit, and I

00:04:00.439 --> 00:04:02.990
saw the angel go down and undo

00:04:02.990 --> 00:04:03.000
his chains.

00:04:03.000 --> 00:04:05.830
There was a

00:04:05.840 --> 00:04:07.309
huge

00:04:07.319 --> 00:04:09.830
lock, and those chains

00:04:09.840 --> 00:04:11.869
came off of him and he started spinning

00:04:11.879 --> 00:04:14.710
like a top all over Europe. He went

00:04:14.720 --> 00:04:16.550
over and started

00:04:16.560 --> 00:04:19.590
influencing Vladimir Putin. Here we

00:04:19.600 --> 00:04:24.670
see North Korea join in with Vladimir

00:04:24.680 --> 00:04:27.710
Putin, sending—some say 3,000 troops,

00:04:27.720 --> 00:04:31.469
some say 11,000 troops—to help

00:04:31.469 --> 00:04:31.479
the

00:04:31.479 --> 00:04:35.270
Russian army with their equipment

00:04:35.280 --> 00:04:36.950
and everything.

00:04:36.960 --> 00:04:39.469
We're seeing an acceleration of war just

00:04:39.479 --> 00:04:41.950
like the Lord warned you was coming,

00:04:41.960 --> 00:04:44.110
and he told me to tell you that this

00:04:44.120 --> 00:04:46.629
is not a time to shrink back; it's

00:04:46.639 --> 00:04:48.510
a time we take more

00:04:48.520 --> 00:04:51.070
land for Jesus. We're going to see

00:04:51.080 --> 00:04:52.830
wars and rumors of wars,

00:05:00.160 --> 00:05:02.189
pestilences, and plagues.

00:05:04.680 --> 00:05:07.110
Men's hearts will fail them

00:05:07.120 --> 00:05:09.029
for fear for looking after those things

00:05:09.039 --> 00:05:11.029
that are coming on the earth, and people

00:05:11.039 --> 00:05:12.710
are going to get all paranoid.

00:05:12.720 --> 00:05:14.310
But

00:05:14.320 --> 00:05:16.950
not the household of faith, not you

00:05:16.960 --> 00:05:18.990
and I, because we have a

00:05:19.000 --> 00:05:21.029
greater covenant. We understand who we

00:05:21.039 --> 00:05:23.110
are in Christ, and we understand that

00:05:23.120 --> 00:05:25.110
greater is He that is in me than he that

00:05:25.120 --> 00:05:27.110
is in the world. We're not of this

00:05:27.120 --> 00:05:29.230
world; we're joint heirs with Jesus

00:05:29.240 --> 00:05:30.510
Christ, seated with Him in the

00:05:30.520 --> 00:05:32.469
heavenlies, far above all principalities

00:05:32.479 --> 00:05:34.990
and powers.

00:05:35.000 --> 00:05:37.110
Anytime I give a word, it's

00:05:37.120 --> 00:05:39.270
never for you to walk in fear; it's

00:05:39.280 --> 00:05:41.230
for you to understand the signs of the

00:05:41.240 --> 00:05:43.230
times.

00:05:46.039 --> 00:05:48.550
You have to get the

00:05:48.560 --> 00:05:51.870
revelation of Psalm 91 and Psalm 23

00:05:51.880 --> 00:05:54.350
inside of your heart like a pillar. You

00:05:54.360 --> 00:05:56.670
need to be rooted and grounded

00:06:01.240 --> 00:06:04.029
in faith. Faith comes by

00:06:04.039 --> 00:06:05.830
hearing, and hearing by the word of God.

00:06:08.199 --> 00:06:10.110
Understanding

00:06:10.120 --> 00:06:11.589
the power and the authority of the name

00:06:11.599 --> 00:06:13.469
of Jesus

00:06:13.469 --> 00:06:13.479
is

00:06:13.479 --> 00:06:15.070
the only way you're going to

00:06:15.080 --> 00:06:17.589
survive what's coming. Great

00:06:17.599 --> 00:06:20.150
dark days are

00:06:20.150 --> 00:06:20.160
coming—gross

00:06:20.160 --> 00:06:22.629
darkness is coming on this

00:06:22.629 --> 00:06:22.639
earth—but

00:06:22.639 --> 00:06:24.710
