00:06:27.189 --> 00:06:27.199
Israel

00:06:27.199 --> 00:06:29.950
in

00:06:29.950 --> 00:06:29.960
Goshen.

00:06:29.960 --> 00:06:31.790
We will have the

00:06:31.800 --> 00:06:33.550
light on us; the light's going to get

00:06:33.560 --> 00:06:35.309
lighter and the dark is going to get

00:06:35.319 --> 00:06:37.469
darker.

00:06:37.479 --> 00:06:39.230
We

00:06:39.240 --> 00:06:41.830
keep our eyes on Jesus because He is our

00:06:41.840 --> 00:06:43.469
Redeemer and the lifter of our

00:06:43.479 --> 00:06:45.790
heads. We get excited about what God

00:06:45.800 --> 00:06:47.430
is doing through you

00:06:47.440 --> 00:06:50.870
and

00:06:50.870 --> 00:06:50.880
me.

00:06:50.880 --> 00:06:53.909
The only Jesus some people will see

00:06:53.919 --> 00:06:57.350
is the Jesus in you and the Jesus in me.

00:07:20.000 --> 00:07:22.589
Let them

00:07:22.599 --> 00:07:25.430
see that glory resonating on you like it

00:07:25.440 --> 00:07:28.749
did Moses. It's called coming up higher

00:07:28.759 --> 00:07:30.029
with the fire.

00:07:33.919 --> 00:07:36.150
He said,

00:07:36.160 --> 00:07:37.909
"Brandon, I want you to remind them

00:07:37.909 --> 00:07:37.919
that

00:07:37.919 --> 00:07:41.790
great sobering days are

00:07:43.950 --> 00:07:43.960
coming."But

00:07:46.280 --> 00:07:49.629
be

00:07:49.639 --> 00:07:52.070
ye filled with the Holy

00:07:52.080 --> 00:07:54.390
Spirit,

00:07:54.400 --> 00:07:56.550
