00:08:05.120 --> 00:08:06.270
I

00:08:06.280 --> 00:08:09.990
love to laugh, like Dick Van

00:08:09.990 --> 00:08:10.000
Dyke

00:08:10.000 --> 00:08:11.309
when they were bouncing on the

00:08:11.319 --> 00:08:12.670
