00:08:15.869 --> 00:08:15.879
ha ha!"Devil,

00:08:15.879 --> 00:08:19.510
you're not

00:08:19.520 --> 00:08:22.550
going to get my joy today;

00:08:22.560 --> 00:08:24.710
I'm bubbling with

00:08:24.720 --> 00:08:26.790
