00:08:26.800 --> 00:08:28.790
We have to

00:08:28.790 --> 00:08:28.800
be

00:08:28.800 --> 00:08:31.629
filled with the Spirit

00:08:31.639 --> 00:08:33.670
because

00:08:33.670 --> 00:08:33.680
of

00:08:33.680 --> 00:08:35.269
those things

00:08:35.279 --> 00:08:37.709
coming upon us. I

00:08:37.709 --> 00:08:37.719
prophesied

00:08:37.719 --> 00:08:39.029
signs in the

00:08:39.029 --> 00:08:39.039
heaven—I

00:08:39.039 --> 00:08:40.829
didn't even

00:08:40.839 --> 00:08:43.269
